#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.DataFrameGroupBy.mf.apply_chunk.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.groupby.DataFrameGroupBy.mf.apply_chunk"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:1 of
msgid ""
"Apply function `func` group-wise and combine the results together. The "
"pandas DataFrame given to the function is a chunk of the input dataframe,"
" consider as a batch rows."
msgstr ""
"按组应用函数 `func` 并将结果合并。传递给函数的 pandas DataFrame 是输入 "
"DataFrame 的一个分块，可视为一批行数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:5 of
msgid ""
"The function passed to `apply` must take a dataframe as its first "
"argument and return a DataFrame, Series or scalar. `apply` will then take"
" care of combining the results back together into a single dataframe or "
"series. `apply` is therefore a highly flexible grouping method."
msgstr ""
"传递给 `apply` 的函数必须以一个 DataFrame 作为第一个参数，并返回一个 "
"DataFrame、Series 或标量。`apply` 会负责将结果合并成一个单独的 DataFrame "
"或 Series。因此，`apply` 是一种非常灵活的分组方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:11 of
msgid ""
"Don't expect to receive all rows of the DataFrame in the function, as it "
"depends on the implementation of MaxFrame and the internal running state "
"of MaxCompute."
msgstr ""
"不要期望在函数中接收到 DataFrame 的所有行，因为这取决于 MaxFrame 的实现和"
" MaxCompute 的内部运行状态。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:15 of
msgid ""
"A callable that takes a dataframe as its first argument, and returns a "
"dataframe, a series or a scalar. In addition the callable may take "
"positional and keyword arguments."
msgstr ""
"一个可调用对象，以 DataFrame 作为第一个参数，并返回一个 DataFrame、Series"
" 或标量。此外，该可调用对象还可以接受位置参数和关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:19 of
msgid ""
"Specify expected number of rows in a batch, as well as the len of "
"function input dataframe. When the remaining data is insufficient, it may"
" be less than this number."
msgstr ""
"指定一个批次中期望的行数，以及函数输入 DataFrame 的长度。当剩余数据不足时"
"，实际行数可能少于该数值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:23 of
msgid "Specify type of returned object. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回对象的类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:25 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrames. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回的 DataFrame 的数据类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:27 of
msgid "Specify dtype of returned Series. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回的 Series 的数据类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:29 of
msgid "Specify name of returned Series. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回的 Series 的名称。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:31 of
msgid "Specify index of returned object. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回对象的索引。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:33 of
msgid "Whether infer dtypes when dtypes or output_type is not specified."
msgstr "当未指定 dtypes 或 output_type 时是否自动推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:35
#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:37 of
msgid "Optional positional and keyword arguments to pass to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的可选位置参数和关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:40 of
msgid "**applied**"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:45 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:46 of
msgid "Apply a function to a Series."
msgstr "对 Series 应用一个函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:48 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:49 of
msgid "Apply a function to each row or column of a DataFrame."
msgstr "对 DataFrame 的每一行或每一列应用一个函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:51 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.mf.apply_chunk`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:52 of
msgid "Apply a function to row batches of a DataFrame."
msgstr "对 DataFrame 的行批次应用一个函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:55 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:56 of
msgid ""
"When deciding output dtypes and shape of the return value, MaxFrame will "
"try applying ``func`` onto a mock grouped object, and the apply call may "
"fail. When this happens, you need to specify the type of apply call "
"(DataFrame or Series) in output_type."
msgstr ""
"在确定返回值的输出数据类型和形状时，MaxFrame 会尝试将 ``func`` 应用于一个"
"模拟的分组对象，此时 apply 调用可能会失败。如果发生这种情况，则需要在 "
"output_type 中指定 apply 调用的类型（DataFrame 或 Series）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:61 of
msgid ""
"For DataFrame output, you need to specify a list or a pandas Series as "
"``dtypes`` of output DataFrame. ``index`` of output can also be "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"对于 DataFrame 输出，你需要指定一个列表或 pandas Series 作为输出 "
"DataFrame 的 ``dtypes``。也可以指定输出的 ``index``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:64 of
msgid ""
"For Series output, you need to specify ``dtype`` and ``name`` of output "
"Series."
msgstr "对于 Series 输出，你需要指定输出 Series 的 ``dtype`` 和 ``name``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply_chunk.df_groupby_apply_chunk:67 of
msgid ""
"MaxFrame adopts expected behavior of pandas>=3.0 by ignoring group "
"columns in user function input. If you still need a group column for your"
" function input, try selecting it right after `groupby` results, for "
"instance, ``df.groupby(\"A\")[[\"A\", \"B\", "
"\"C\"]].mf.apply_batch(func)`` will pass data of column A into ``func``."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame 采用 pandas>=3.0 的预期行为，在用户函数输入中忽略分组列。如果你"
"仍需要将分组列传递给函数，可以在 `groupby` 结果后立即选择该列，例如 ``df."
"groupby(\"A\")[[\"A\", \"B\", \"C\"]].mf.apply_batch(func)`` 会将列 A 的"
"数据传递给 ``func``。"

